---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="404 - El gatito se ha perdido | Ágatha Gatos Persas"
  description="Página no encontrada. Parece que el gatito se ha ido a otra sección de la web."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-[#FDFCFB] flex items-center justify-center pt-20 pb-20 px-4 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 -left-20 w-64 h-64 bg-[#FFE2E2] rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50 -z-10"></div>
    <div class="max-md:hidden absolute bottom-1/4 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-amber-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40 -z-10"></div>

    <section class="max-lg:mt-20 max-w-[1100px] w-full relative">
      
      <div class="absolute -top-20 lg:-top-32 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 opacity-[0.08] select-none pointer-events-none">
        <span class="text-[200px] md:text-[350px] font-black text-[#FF6B6B] leading-none tracking-tighter">404</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left space-y-8">
          <div>
            <span class="bg-[#FF6B6B] text-white text-[10px] font-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-[0.2em] shadow-lg shadow-pink-200">
              Oops! El gatito se ha ido
            </span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] mt-6">
              Página no <br/> <span class="text-[#FF6B6B]">encontrada.</span>
            </h1>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-medium max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed italic">
            "Parece que este enlace se ha quedado dormido o ha decidido explorar un rincón que todavía no existe."
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="/" class="bg-[#FF6B6B] text-white font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-pink-100 hover:shadow-gray-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
              Volver al Inicio
            </a>
            <a href="/principal/gatos-disponibles" class="border-2 border-gray-200 text-gray-700 font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:border-[#FF6B6B] hover:text-[#FF6B6B] transition-all">
              Ver Gatitos
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose">
              ¿Crees que es un error? <br/>
              <a href="/principal/contacto" class="text-[#FF6B6B] hover:underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4">Avísanos para que lo arreglemos</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full max-w-sm">
          <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500 border border-gray-100">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 border border-dashed border-gray-200 flex flex-col items-center">
              
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl mb-6 relative group">
                <span class="text-4xl group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">🐾</span>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-2 border-[#FF6B6B] animate-ping opacity-20"></div>
              </div>

              <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 text-center uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">
                Ficha de Extravío
              </h2>
              
              <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[#FF6B6B] mb-6 rounded-full"></div>

              <ul class="w-full space-y-4">
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Nombre</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 italic">Enlace Roto</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Estado</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Buscando hogar</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Sugerencia</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-[#FF6B6B]">Pulsa el botón rosa</span>
                </li>
              </ul>

              <div class="mt-8 text-[10px] text-center text-gray-400 font-medium leading-relaxed italic">
                "Ningún gatito persa fue dañado durante la carga de esta página inexistente."
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
</style>